phicBuffer.ConvertStringToBinary(strIn, BinaryStringEncoding.Utf16LE);\n\n    // Convert the string to UTF8 binary data.\n    IBuffer buffUTF8 = CryptographicBuffer.ConvertStringToBinary(strIn, BinaryStringEncoding.Utf8);\n}\n```\n\n \n\n \n\n\n\n\n"}